children.name: Rules
children.text:
Buried with the remains of Thisseeu, this staff is suffused with their power and constantly grows moss all over the root bulb at its top. 
While attuned to this staff the spell save DC for all of your transmutation and conjuration spells are increased by 1. You also gain access to the Primal Savagery cantrip.
This staff has 5 charges and regains them all daily at dawn. The staff also regains a single charge whenever you completely change your form. The charges can be used to cast:
Animal Friendship (1 charge)      Speak with Animals (1 charge)
Alter Self (2 charges)                     Healing Spirit (3 charges)
